---
import DraftLayout from '../../layouts/DraftLayout.astro';
---
<DraftLayout title="Spinal Energetics — Subtle Somatics" description="A subtle-and-powerful modality working with your body's natural intelligence through touch, sound and movement." activeNav="spinal">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Spinal Energetics</p>
      <h1 class="reveal">The Language of the Living Current</h1>
      <p class="reveal" data-delay="100">Everything in us moves in spirals, in waves, in gentle fluctuations that know their own rhythm. In this natural movement lies the wisdom of unfolding.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="content-split">
      <div class="content-text reveal-left">
        <h2>Working with your body's natural intelligence</h2>
        <p>Spinal Energetics follows the natural, cyclical dynamic of energy and consciousness. Through mindful impulses and intuitive guidance, tensions dissolve in an organic way, while hidden resources become palpable on their own.</p>
        <p>At your core, you are strength, love, radiance and trust — and so many more qualities of resourcefulness. Imagine a treasure chest full of gems — each gem another nuance of resourcefulness that you can increasingly embody. It is already there. And often it is concealed by tension patterns of various kinds — emotional, physical, mental and spiritual.</p>
        <p>I invite you into a safe and courageous space so that these tension patterns may move and shift — and more and more of who you truly are can unfold.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-image reveal-right">
        <img src="/images/spinal-energetics.png" alt="Spinal Energetics" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-surface">
    <div class="section" style="padding-top:4rem;padding-bottom:4rem;">
      <h2 class="text-center reveal" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">In a session, you may experience</h2>
      <div class="experience-grid">
        <div class="exp-card card-shine reveal" data-delay="0">
          <h3>Deep surrender</h3>
          <p>Deep relaxation and restoration — your nervous system settling into safety.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="exp-card card-shine reveal" data-delay="100">
          <h3>Spontaneous movement</h3>
          <p>Your body unwinding on its own — subtle or strong physical movements as energy shifts and reorganises.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="exp-card card-shine reveal" data-delay="200">
          <h3>Emotional release</h3>
          <p>Stored tension and emotional patterns dissolving — making space for clarity and renewed connection.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="exp-card card-shine reveal" data-delay="300">
          <h3>Expansion</h3>
          <p>A sense of spaciousness, grounding, or both — feeling more alive, more connected, more yourself.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center reveal" data-delay="400" style="margin:3rem auto 0;color:var(--text-muted);font-style:italic;max-width:600px;">This work is not about fixing or striving — it's about entering the field where what's true begins to reveal itself, in its own rhythm and time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="session-info text-center">
      <h2 class="reveal">Sessions</h2>
      <div class="format-grid reveal" data-delay="150">
        <div class="format-card card-shine">
          <h3>1:1 Sessions</h3>
          <p>In person or online — you remain fully clothed, lying on a massage table. Through gentle touch and intuitive presence, your body responds naturally.</p>
          <p class="format-detail">~60 min &middot; &euro;130</p>
        </div>
        <div class="format-card card-shine">
          <h3>Group Experiences</h3>
          <p>Amplifying resonance through collective energy — the field of a group deepens the work for everyone present.</p>
          <p class="format-detail">Coming soon</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contraindications -->
  <section class="contraindications-section">
    <div class="contraindications-inner reveal">
      <h2>Important health information</h2>
      <p class="contra-intro">Your health comes first. Please read under which circumstances Spinal Energetics is not suitable:</p>
      <ul class="contra-list">
        <li>Pregnancy in the 1st or 3rd trimester, and up to 6 months postpartum</li>
        <li>Age under 12 or over 75</li>
        <li>Bipolar disorder, schizophrenia, or psychotic episodes</li>
        <li>Severe PTSD</li>
        <li>Epilepsy or conditions with seizure risk</li>
        <li>Severe cardiovascular conditions</li>
        <li>Severe asthma</li>
        <li>Recent fractures, injuries, or surgeries</li>
        <li>Psychiatric hospitalization or acute crisis within the last 3 years</li>
        <li>Use of multiple strong psychotropic medications</li>
        <li>Participation under the influence of psychoactive substances</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="contra-note">Please contact me at <a href="mailto:connect@subtlesomatics.space">connect@subtlesomatics.space</a> if you're unsure whether any of these apply to you — we'll look at it together.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section-surface">
    <div class="section" style="padding-top:4rem;padding-bottom:4rem;">
      <h2 class="text-center reveal" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">Questions about Spinal Energetics</h2>
      <div class="faq-container reveal" data-delay="150">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What happens in a session?</summary>
          <p>You remain fully clothed, lying on a massage table. Through gentle touch and intuitive presence, your body responds naturally — sometimes with subtle shifts, sometimes with dynamic movements. Sessions typically begin with arriving in stillness together.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How many sessions do I need?</summary>
          <p>Every body responds uniquely. Some feel deep change after one session; others find that a series supports deeper integration. Often 3-6 sessions offer a strong foundation.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What do people experience?</summary>
          <p>Clients often describe deep relaxation, emotional release, heightened clarity, and renewed connection to their body. Movements may arise spontaneously, or the experience may be more internal and quiet. Many people experience warmth, tingling, and a sense of deep aliveness.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Is it safe?</summary>
          <p>Yes. The process honors your body's wisdom. Nothing is forced; your body sets the pace.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Who is it for?</summary>
          <p>For anyone longing for deeper embodiment, release of stored tension, and connection to their inner vitality. It's supportive for those in transition, healers, creatives, and seekers of wholeness.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Are there contraindications?</summary>
          <p>Yes — please see the "Important health information" section above. If you're unsure whether any apply to you, reach out and we'll look at it together.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How does integration work?</summary>
          <p>Integration continues after the session as your body reorganises. You may feel more spacious, tired, or energized. Gentle self-care, rest, journaling, time in nature, and hydration support this natural process.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Booking -->
  <section class="section booking-section">
    <div class="booking-inner reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow text-center">Take the first step</p>
      <h2 class="text-center">Ready to experience it?</h2>
      <p class="text-center booking-sub">All that's required is openness and willingness to receive.</p>
      <div class="cal-embed-wrapper">
        <iframe src="https://cal.com/subtlesomatics/discovery" style="width:100%;height:700px;border:none;" loading="lazy" title="Book a discovery call with Subtle Somatics"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</DraftLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero { background: var(--bg-surface); padding: 10rem 2rem 6rem; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .page-hero-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .page-hero h1 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .page-hero p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.15rem; margin: 0 auto; }
  .eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }

  .content-split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .content-image img { border-radius: 2px; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
  .content-text h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .content-text p { margin-bottom: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }

  .experience-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .exp-card { padding: 2rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .exp-card h3 { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .exp-card p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .format-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; max-width: 700px; margin: 2rem auto 0; }
  .format-card { padding: 2rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: center; }
  .format-card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .format-card p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0 auto; }
  .format-detail { font-size: 0.8rem !important; color: var(--accent) !important; margin-top: 1rem !important; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; }

  /* Contraindications */
  .contraindications-section {
    background: var(--bg-warm);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .contraindications-inner {
    max-width: 750px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(196, 164, 108, 0.2);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    background: rgba(196, 164, 108, 0.03);
  }
  .contraindications-inner h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .contra-intro {
    color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .contra-list {
    list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .contra-list li {
    padding: 0.6rem 0 0.6rem 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    position: relative;
  }
  .contra-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .contra-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; left: 0; top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  .contra-note {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    padding: 1rem;
    background: rgba(196, 164, 108, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196, 164, 108, 0.1);
  }
  .contra-note a { color: var(--accent); }

  .faq-container { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .faq-item summary { padding: 1.25rem 0; font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-primary); cursor: pointer; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .faq-item summary::after { content: '+'; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-left: 1rem; }
  .faq-item[open] summary::after { content: '\2212'; }
  .faq-item summary:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .faq-item p { padding: 0 0 1.5rem; color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; max-width: none; }

  /* Booking */
  .booking-section { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .booking-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .booking-sub { color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 1rem auto 2.5rem; }
  .cal-embed-wrapper {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .content-image { max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto; order: -1; }
    .experience-grid, .format-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
